f=Engineering/axiom/custom/dsa-design-records/assets/dsa-record-template.md · h1:DSA Design Record DSR-[NNN] [choice name]=ADR algorithms/data structures. Append-only; reversal new DSR citing one. Credit: pattern dev/architecture-decisions. **Status:** proposed accepted superseded-by DSR-NNN **Date:** YYYY-MM-DD **Reviewed by:** [raj/dana/…] · h2:Operations matter (start here)=\| operation \| frequency \| latency sensitivity \| · h2:Operations matter (start here)=\|---\|---\|---\| · h2:Operations matter (start here)=\| [lookup / range / insert / ordered-iter / delete] \| [hot/warm/cold] \| \| · h2:Options considered (2+)=\| option \| time (worst / amortized) \| space \| justifying invariant \| notes \| · h2:Options considered (2+)=\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\| · h2:Options considered (2+)=\| A: [structure] \| \| \| [why the bound holds] \| \| · h2:Options considered (2+)=\| B: [structure] \| \| \| \| \| · h2:Decision=[chosen option] because [the operation mix constraints select it]. · h2:Trade-offs kept (the reasons someone later want change this)=[cost chosen structure e.g., ordering memory overhead rebalance cost] · h2:Complexity summary (the claim, checkable)=[operation]: O(…) [worst], O(…) [amortized] because [invariant], constants real-n dominate asymptotics: [note performance-profiling ref] · h2:Supersedes / superseded by=[DSR-refs]